Place the egg plant inside the fridge.

Place the eggplant in the fridge.

Take an eggplant from the top of the sink.
Move towards the right and reach the sink.
Put the eggplant in the sink, wash it and take it out.

Open the fridge and put the eggplant inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the eggplant inside the fridge
